# S4 method for DownSamplingConsensusPartition
get_anno(object, reduce = FALSE)

Arguments

object

A DownSamplingConsensusPartition-class object.
reduce

Used internally.

Value

A data frame if anno was specified in consensus_partition_by_down_sampling, or else NULL.

Author

Zuguang Gu <z.gu@dkfz.de>

data(golub_cola_ds)
get_anno(golub_cola_ds)
